[SPEAKER_00]: We'll go ahead and go to those and let you talk about each one of them, some photographs.

14:21.085 --> 14:22.948
[SPEAKER_00]: I think we're ready to go right now.

14:22.988 --> 14:26.154
[SPEAKER_00]: This is a photograph that I took a photograph of.

14:26.194 --> 14:28.337
[SPEAKER_00]: Talk about what we're looking at there.

