[SPEAKER_01]: That's taken right outside of Da Nang there, what they call Happy Valley or Arizona Territory.

14:38.214 --> 14:40.838
[SPEAKER_01]: And I was 26 years old there.

14:40.858 --> 14:45.124
[SPEAKER_01]: I was a platoon sergeant of Alpha Company, 1st Battalion, 3rd Marines.

14:46.306 --> 14:57.363
[SPEAKER_01]: And that's what we tried to help the South Vietnamese, where the Vietcon come at night and they threaten to kill the women and children if they didn't fight for them.

14:57.383 --> 14:58.645
[SPEAKER_01]: So we tried to protect them.

14:59.603 --> 15:09.906
[SPEAKER_01]: We're in the hearts and minds of the Vietnamese because Charlie, the VC, always come in and took part of their food or took ransom from them.

15:10.788 --> 15:14.997
[SPEAKER_01]: So we guarded them and I had a combat photographer and he took that picture.

15:15.263 --> 15:16.044
[SPEAKER_00]: And put it together.

15:16.064 --> 15:21.251
[SPEAKER_01]: And I had it developed in Okinawa, and I pulled back there to pick up new replacements.

15:21.271 --> 15:24.155
[SPEAKER_01]: Okay, let's move on to the next one.

15:24.175 --> 15:28.921
[SPEAKER_00]: This is a picture that's shown a little wear and tear over the year, but there's a Marine West.

15:29.141 --> 15:38.073
[SPEAKER_01]: That's a machine gun that was involved in saving a few Marines' lives in Vietnam, and a combat photographer wanted to take that picture.

15:38.093 --> 15:44.882
[SPEAKER_01]: And that was taken on the USS Okinawa, LPH landing platform, HILO, that was a World War II

15:45.605 --> 15:49.591
[SPEAKER_01]: Aircraft carrier for prop planes.

15:49.611 --> 15:51.694
[SPEAKER_01]: So he gave me a copy of it.

15:53.436 --> 15:56.020
[SPEAKER_01]: And that's when I was still pretty good and strong.

15:56.040 --> 15:58.904
[SPEAKER_01]: When I'd been shot up too bad or busted up.

16:00.426 --> 16:01.508
[SPEAKER_01]: All right.

16:01.528 --> 16:05.313
[SPEAKER_01]: That's what we call in Vietnam.

16:05.333 --> 16:08.558
[SPEAKER_01]: They had Catholic little churches.

